profile:
Maple Leaf Residential Cleaners offers your HOME comprehensive cleaning.

We understand the cleaning requirements of each home is unique.  We will provide you a quote over the phone or email.

HEALTH & SAFETY of our Team and Valued Clients is paramount during this Pandemic.  To learn more about 'Commitment to Cleanliness' - please visit the HEALTH & SAFETY page on our website underneath Commercial Cleaning tab.

We provide the following services for your home/apartment/condominiums:
+ One time cleaning (with option to book the Standard Maple Leaf Cleaning or Deep Cleaning)
+ Recurring cleaning (weekly/biweekly/monthly) for our Valued Clients
+ Post-Construction or Post-Renovation Deep Cleaning
+ Window Cleaning (interior & exterior including screens & tracks)
+ Carpet shampoo

Our cleaners cover all areas:
+ bathrooms and powder rooms
+ bedrooms (including changing sheets for recurring clients)
+ living and dining room
+ dens and common areas
+ kitchen 
+ deep cleaning services of fridge/oven
+ windows, doors, walls and baseboards
+ carpeted areas vacuumed
+ floors swept and mopped
+ dusting furniture, lamp shades and fixture

Meeting your needs is our promise and exceeding your expectations is our goal.

#MapleLeafResidentialCleaners

Prime Care Cleaning Services is a well established licensed and insured Canadian company offering a variety of professional cleaning services to home owners in Peel Region and the Greater Toronto area.

We have developed a specialized system to assist homeowners and businesses with all their cleaning needs. With our own network of professional maids, who are skilled and well trained, and ready to work side-by-side with you, to ensure that you receive a high level of personalized service to assure your complete satisfaction.

We will also assist you with proper selection of the best cleaning products available and handle all other necessary details to make your house cleaning to go as smoothly as possible.

Our service is always courteous, professional and competitive. You are welcomed to shop around and get an estimate but if you are really ready to SAVE NOW, call us and we’ll beat the competition. profile:
Whether your company is a large Fortune 500 or a small start up, we can create a cleaning service program to suit your specific needs and budget. Whatever frequency of cleaning you require — daily, weekly, monthly or even one-time-only — SM janitor custom tailors each and every cleaning program to ensure the most economical service.

Learn more about our programs.

We put our reputation on the line every day, which means that we are not satisfied with our cleaning services unless you are. Our employees are trained in the most modern and effective professional office cleaning techniques as well as product usage and safety procedures. On-site inspections by our team of supervisors ensure that all cleaning service plans are performed to the highest level of service.

RESTROOM SANITIZING AND DEEP CLEANING. 

Disinfecting, deodorizing and scouring all lavatory fixtures including basins, toilets, urinals etc.
Sanitizing and mopping lavatory floors with a disinfectant to kill bacteria and odors
Sanitizing all counters, vanities and powder shelves
Cleaning and polishing all mirrors, bridgework and plumbing equipment
Washing toilet seats, top, underside and hinges
Spot cleaning walls and partitions
Cleaning and sanitizing light switches, doorknobs and handles
Cleaning lavatory dispensers and receptacles
Emptying waste receptacles and replacing liners

RESTAURANT DEEP CLEANING SERVICES 

Washing and sanitizing sinks, faucets and countertops
Mopping, scrubbing and drying of floor
Emptying, cleaning and sanitizing trash receptacles
Cleaning inside surfaces of microwave oven and refrigerator
Cleaning outside surfaces of appliances such as refrigerator, microwave, coffee maker and toaster oven
Cleaning outside faces of cabinets
Refilling towel, soap and tissue dispensers

FLOOR CARE SERVICES 

Ensure the appearance and cleanliness of your floors with SM janitor professional floor cleaning service. Our floor cleaning and preventative maintenance program will keep even high-traffic surfaces looking their best by minimizing the impact of wear and tear and preventing nicks and scratches.

Over time dirt and grit can damage floors, which can lead to costly floor replacement. The experts at SM janitor have the experience to assess your needs and recommend the appropriate course of actin, such as high-speed polishing, honing, waxing and sealing, or grinding.
